N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4603.9 - Effective date of license

State Regulations

No license for the conduct of any game of chance shall be
effective for a period of more than one year from the date of original
issuance. No license, after its issuance, shall be amended so as to render it
valid beyond a period of one year from the date of its original
issuance. Notes
